Havent updated in awhile.  Recently things have been good.  I dont even know why I type in this thing.  Ive been on this site for along time (off and on for the past 4 years. with like 3 diff names).  I guess its nice to sit online, listen to music, and talk write shit about your life.

 

Anyways tonight, Charlie and myself hung out.  Got some Jomoccah(spelling??) shakes from Arbys, went to CVS, then to Jims.  Also he let me borrow his Hellfest 2002 DVD.  The only thing I want to watch again was the Bane footage of "Can we start again".  AMAZING.  Too bad Hellfest is going  downhill. 

Latley Ive been on a Jomoccah shake craze. 

So I got a new plan to wake up in the morning.  Remember when you were younger how you would wake up, watch cartoons, eat cereal, than go to school.  Well Im going to start doing that again. The problem is that  THERE IS NO FUCKING GOOD MORNING CARTOONS ANYMORE.    I swear to god, all the cartoons suck nowadays.

So Im going to download ALL the LEGEND OF ZELDA, and SUPER MARIO 3 / SUPER MARIO SUPER SHOW CARTOONS.   So heres going to be my new schedule:

4:50 - Wake up, workout!

5:50 - Shower, get dressed, and get cereal ready!

6:00 - Watch my cartoons, and eat some cereal. Until 7:00

7:00 - Go to school.

 

This is a great plan!
